Package de.hsrt.holbox.EnhancedPowerFlow

package de.hsrt.holbox.EnhancedPowerFlow
This package contains all structures needed to conduct an enhanced power flow calculation as described in ICREPQ'23 paper
  • Class

    Bus
    Represents a bus in the system
    PowerFlowProblem
    The main class necessary to solve an enhanced power flow calculation problem
